fields.inlineHelpText:
Edit this email message Text (up to 10,000 characters) and it will appear in the notification to sign for
			your DocuSign Recipient.
fields.label: Email message
fields.name: dfsle__EmailMessage__c

fields.inlineHelpText:
Change this default email subject text and it will appear as the Subject Line in the notification to Sign
			for your DocuSign Recipients.
fields.label: Email subject
fields.name: dfsle__EmailSubject__c

fields.inlineHelpText: The configuration used to generate this envelope.
fields.label: Envelope Configuration
fields.name: dfsle__EnvelopeConfiguration__c

fields.inlineHelpText: Indicate the number of days until this transaction is expired.
fields.label: Expire/void envelope in N day(s)
fields.name: dfsle__ExpireAfterDays__c

fields.inlineHelpText:
Indicate how many days prior to expiration you want an email message to alert recipients that a deadline
			approaches for completion. This is sent only to recipients who have not yet completed the transaction.
fields.label: Warn of expiration in N day(s) prior
fields.name: dfsle__ExpireWarnDays__c

fields.inlineHelpText: At times, you may need to encourage your recipients to complete an envelope more rapidly. After an envelope expires, DocuSign voids the envelope and sends a notification to both sender and recipient.
fields.label: Expire/void Envelope
fields.name: dfsle__Expires__c

fields.inlineHelpText: Indicate how many days should pass before the first reminder is sent
fields.label: Send reminder in N day(s)
fields.name: dfsle__RemindAfterDays__c

fields.inlineHelpText: Indicate how often (in days) the reminder should repeat until the transaction is complete.
fields.label: Remind every N day(s) until complete
fields.name: dfsle__RemindFrequencyDays__c

fields.inlineHelpText:
Check this box to have an email reminder sent to recipients of the envelope who have not yet completed
			their task.
fields.label: Remind signers via email
fields.name: dfsle__Remind__c

fields.inlineHelpText: Check to show chatter during DocuSign signature workflow.
fields.label: Enable Chatter status updates
fields.name: dfsle__UpdateChatter__c
